e=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Shop window\"\n        title=\"Shop window\"\n        src=\"/static/cc389f588e0d04b01a7d03af5c4725fc/c35de/greatNorthPieCo-015.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/cc389f588e0d04b01a7d03af5c4725fc/afcd2/greatNorthPieCo-015.jpg 300w,\n/static/cc389f588e0d04b01a7d03af5c4725fc/82472/greatNorthPieCo-015.jpg 600w,\n/static/cc389f588e0d04b01a7d03af5c4725fc/c35de/greatNorthPieCo-015.jpg 1200w,\n/static/cc389f588e0d04b01a7d03af5c4725fc/98235/greatNorthPieCo-015.jpg 1800w,\n/static/cc389f588e0d04b01a7d03af5c4725fc/36a65/greatNorthPieCo-015.jpg 2100w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n</div></figure>\n<figure class=\"markdown-grid\"><div class=\"markdown-grid-grid\" style=\"\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(48%, 1fr));\n          \">\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Cafe interior\"\n        title=\"Cafe interior\"\n        src=\"/static/2accb0ba816835c0575779b57ca3555e/c35de/greatNorthPieCo-001.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2accb0ba816835c0575779b57ca3555e/afcd2/greatNorthPieCo-001.jpg 300w,\n/static/2accb0ba816835c0575779b57ca3555e/82472/greatNorthPieCo-001.jpg 600w,\n/static/2accb0ba816835c0575779b57ca3555e/c35de/greatNorthPieCo-001.jpg 1200w,\n/static/2accb0ba816835c0575779b57ca3555e/98235/greatNorthPieCo-001.jpg 1800w,\n/static/2accb0ba816835c0575779b57ca3555e/36a65/greatNorthPieCo-001.jpg 2100w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Window seating\"\n        title=\"Window seating\"\n        src=\"/static/240c7c7e91928d025047d593d66d9934/c35de/greatNorthPieCo-002.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/240c7c7e91928d025047d593d66d9934/afcd2/greatNorthPieCo-002.jpg 300w,\n/static/240c7c7e91928d025047d593d66d9934/82472/greatNorthPieCo-002.jpg 600w,\n/static/240c7c7e91928d025047d593d66d9934/c35de/greatNorthPieCo-002.jpg 1200w,\n/static/240c7c7e91928d025047d593d66d9934/98235/greatNorthPieCo-002.jpg 1800w,\n/static/240c7c7e91928d025047d593d66d9934/36a65/greatNorthPieCo-002.jpg 2100w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n</div></figure>\n<h3>Learning to make pies</h3>\n<p>Neil’s passion for comfort food echoes back to his childhood memories when his mum used to work in a bakery and bring home pasties.  After graduating from university Neil began working in restaurants alongside Michelin star chefs.  Then after travelling for a while he came back and joined the Greater Manchester police force, though an underlying desire to pursue a culinary career still remained. </p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>“I always knew I wanted to come back into it full-time.  I was just thinking of different ideas to get back into food, and I saw an advertisement for a farmers’ market.  I phoned them up and told them I had an idea to make pasties and they said to come down next month.”</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>At this point Neil hadn’t even begun making pies so he began teaching himself to make pastry and practicing in his spare time.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>“I made a few pasties and they came out alright, then I got some tins and tried making pies and they started coming out a bit better.  And then I went to the farmers’ market. I’d tried putting it off but in the end I just went for it.  I think I made about 15 pies, went there and sold those.  I was over the moon”</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Farmers’ markets across the north of England became Neil’s stomping ground.  For several years he worked on the business part-time; making pies at home and taking them to the markets every weekend.  Still gradually learning, Neil was able to get feedback from customers at the markets.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>“It takes you to lots of different areas. It’s quite nice in a way, you don’t have to invest in a building or have a shop where you’re quite static.  You’re almost testing the market and seeing how it works.”</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Now working on the business full-time, Neil still regularly attends markets across the north of England.  The Great North Pie Co is resident at Altrinchams’s Market House, a highly successful food hall offering a range of the finest food &#x26; drink in the Manchester area.  In 2017, the café was opened in Ambleside and has since been a great success.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>“We always wanted to run our own little café and we always wanted to open in the Lakes. It’s a great place to serve this kind of comfort food – go for a walk, come back get a pie &#x26; mash, a couple of beers.”</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>The prospect of being able to showcase local produce to the tourists that come to Ambleside also appealed to Neil.</p>\n<figure class=\"markdown-grid\"><div class=\"markdown-grid-grid\" style=\"\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(98%, 1fr));\n          \">\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Beef &amp; Potato Pie Detail\"\n        title=\"Beef &amp; Potato Pie Detail\"\n        src=\"/static/4fd4e4d56fc35906b4610a9f97135015/c35de/greatNorthPieCo-018.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4fd4e4d56fc35906b4610a9f97135015/afcd2/greatNorthPieCo-018.jpg 300w,\n/static/4fd4e4d56fc35906b4610a9f97135015/82472/greatNorthPieCo-018.jpg 600w,\n/static/4fd4e4d56fc35906b4610a9f97135015/c35de/greatNorthPieCo-018.jpg 1200w,\n/static/4fd4e4d56fc35906b4610a9f97135015/98235/greatNorthPieCo-018.jpg 1800w,\n/static/4fd4e4d56fc35906b4610a9f97135015/36a65/greatNorthPieCo-018.jpg 2100w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n</div></figure>\n<figure class=\"markdown-grid\"><div class=\"markdown-grid-grid\" style=\"\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(48%, 1fr));\n          \">\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Neil Broomfield Portrait\"\n        title=\"Neil Broomfield Portrait\"\n        src=\"/static/c50c0141ee5fc4fa8063133275330683/c35de/greatNorthPieCo-010.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c50c0141ee5fc4fa8063133275330683/afcd2/greatNorthPieCo-010.jpg 300w,\n/static/c50c0141ee5fc4fa8063133275330683/82472/greatNorthPieCo-010.jpg 600w,\n/static/c50c0141ee5fc4fa8063133275330683/c35de/greatNorthPieCo-010.jpg 1200w,\n/static/c50c0141ee5fc4fa8063133275330683/98235/greatNorthPieCo-010.jpg 1800w,\n/static/c50c0141ee5fc4fa8063133275330683/36a65/greatNorthPieCo-010.jpg 2100w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Gravy being added to a pie\"\n        title=\"Gravy being added to a pie\"\n        src=\"/static/5e5dc033302d6bd45dd30583383d2a8f/c35de/greatNorthPieCo-021.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5e5dc033302d6bd45dd30583383d2a8f/afcd2/greatNorthPieCo-021.jpg 300w,\n/static/5e5dc033302d6bd45dd30583383d2a8f/82472/greatNorthPieCo-021.jpg 600w,\n/static/5e5dc033302d6bd45dd30583383d2a8f/c35de/greatNorthPieCo-021.jpg 1200w,\n/static/5e5dc033302d6bd45dd30583383d2a8f/98235/greatNorthPieCo-021.jpg 1800w,\n/static/5e5dc033302d6bd45dd30583383d2a8f/36a65/greatNorthPieCo-021.jpg 2100w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n</div></figure>\n<h3>A showcase of high quality, local produce</h3>\n<p>The Great North Pie Co strives to to provide a product that is of high quality, using local produce.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>“It’s all about quality, it’s not about numbers.  I don’t think you want to be eating pies every day but when you do it’s got to be a treat, it’s got to be something special.”</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Some notable ingredients currently on the menu include Swaledale native British beef(Corned beef cured for ten days), Lancashire cheese, &#x26; Stornoway black pudding.  There’s a huge emphasis on the use of local produce, an ethos that Neil wanted to reflect whilst naming the company.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>“We try to take everything from Yorkshire, Cumbria, and the rest of the north-west and try to highlight and promote them along the way.  We’re just trying to do something on a regional scale.  But I think the main thing is that it’s got to be good, quality produce.”</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>And the quality of products made by the Great North Pie Co has been recognized on multiple occasions – having received awards from the British Pie Awards and the BBC Food &#x26; Farming Awards.</p>\n<p>Having now pushed the company to a sustainable level, and having been recognized as a producer of great-tasting quality pies, Neil intends to keep focused on the quality of food, customer service and providing exceptional versions of this symbolic product of England’s north-west.</p>\n<figure class=\"markdown-grid\"><div class=\"markdown-grid-grid\" style=\"\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(48%, 1fr));\n          \">\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        